        {
            "title": "葵涌動物醫院揭貓咪離奇受傷死亡 警拘37歲男貓主",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"動物醫院發現求醫貓隻有可疑傷勢並死亡，警方拘捕男貓主。林思明攝\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/096b5a6d6601dc7682e1afcfe3b5896a/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250218/_2025021811140484521.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">動物醫院發現求醫貓隻有可疑傷勢並死亡，警方拘捕男貓主。林思明攝</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>葵涌發生虐待動物案。今日（18日）清晨6時許，警方接獲葵豐街2至52號地下一間動物醫院的職員報案，指一名男子帶同一隻貓咪到來求醫，但貓隻有可疑傷勢並死亡。警方經調查後，列作殘酷對待動物案件，拘捕37歲男貓主。\n\n</p>\n<p>現場是豐盈動物專科及急症醫院。據了解，涉事死亡的貓隻已成年，昨晚牠被一名男子抱到動物醫院求醫，當時貓隻已滿身鮮血奄奄一息，動物醫院獸醫經檢查後，發現貓隻有不尋常傷勢，其後貓隻更死亡，動物醫院職員於是報警。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"none-100\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4087237/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"貓咪被帶到動物醫院求醫，但牠滿身傷痕，最終死亡。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f6c966b3b4ab8682f4fd60d64bf304b3/2025-02/1_1_49.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        貓咪被帶到動物醫院求醫，但牠滿身傷痕，最終死亡。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4087218/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"現場是豐盈動物專科及急症醫院。林思明攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/513f8c2460b9b2d4f4fc12e6da987663/2025-02/KakaoTalk_20250218_105324019.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        現場是豐盈動物專科及急症醫院。林思明攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4087219/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/6693773870e026a5d61dff80816777f1/2025-02/KakaoTalk_20250218_105324019_01.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4087220/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/72af19eebd433801bcaf77f972c80087/2025-02/KakaoTalk_20250218_105324019_02.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4087221/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"事件由動物醫院揭發。林思明\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/e6df1c1738dc6d6959cbbd0c55be2b98/2025-02/KakaoTalk_20250218_105423571.jp